                            <comment id="12937471" author="rnewson" created="Tue, 7 Mar 2006 20:02:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;moved into activemq package and assigned copyright to Apache.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This test should probably catch OOM and assert rather than just crashing...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12937534" author="chirino" created="Tue, 7 Mar 2006 21:05:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Root case:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When client used a ranged ack, only the last message in the range was being deleted from the message store.  For the peristent store case, this could be the cause of some other performance issues since the journal and long term were holding on to messages longer than they needed to.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
